        "5H" to """This card indicates that a major change is coming to you, your home, or your family. This change could be a possible divorce, or a loved one moving away, or even a change of residence i.e. a new home.""",
        "6H" to """This card generally shows a time of peace and harmony where you can work well with others to achieve your goals and overcome obstacles.""",
